   _ Laser-guided 'smart' bombs, $75,000 each
</P>
<P>
   _ Downed F-117 Stealth fighter plane, $45 million
</P>
<P>
   _ Use of two B-2 Stealth bombers for two sorties, $6.4 million
</P>
<P>
   _ Humanitarian assistance to refugees, $91 million last year
plus $50 million newly authorized
</P>
