<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-02 13:31 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3741 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SCI-CELL-REPAIR-ART-B     04-02 0974
