<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-02 16:46 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3983 &Cx1f; tab-z
r e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NYTBOOK-BUNDY-1000&AMP;AD     04-02 4067
