Serena Williams have been saying they'd reach the top all along.
Now they're starting to back it up. Their cocky attitude turned off
other players _ especially veterans _ at first, but have feelings
toward them changed? Also talking to coaches and players about
their chances of pulling off their prediction a 1-2 in the world
rankings sister act. (Holcomb, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). MOVED
